#: ../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/faq.rst:50
msgid ""
"Knowing the encoding of the source file: calibre tries to guess what "
"character encoding your source files use, but often, this is impossible, so "
"you need to tell it what encoding to use. This can be done in the GUI via "
"the :guilabel:`Input character encoding` field in the :guilabel:`Look & "
